00:04:27.904 --> 00:04:32.261
or you can click Browse to find a picture that you have your system that

93
00:04:32.261 --> 00:04:33.963
maybe you've downloaded from the internet.

94
00:04:33.963 --> 00:04:37.260
If it is a picture, you can choose whether you want to tile it,

95
00:04:37.260 --> 00:04:38.357
stretch it, fit it,

96
00:04:38.357 --> 00:04:41.433
it's going to depend upon the screen resolution that you're using.

97
00:04:41.433 --> 00:04:43.492
If you're using a solid color background,

98
00:04:43.492 --> 00:04:44.945
that's one of the options here,

99
00:04:44.945 --> 00:04:47.758
